<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="NTM10.7">
<l>naṭamāṭit tōkai virikkiṉṟa māmayil kāḷummai</l>
<l>naṭamāṭṭaṅ kāṇap pāviyē ṉāṉōr mutalilēṉ</l>
<l>kuṭamāṭu kūttaṉ kōvintaṉ kōmiṟai ceytemmai</l>
<l>uṭaimāṭu koṇṭā ṉuṅkaḷuk kiṉiyoṉṟu pōtumē</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>O great peacocks that dance and spread out [your] plumage!</l>
<l>I, a sinner, do not have the basis to see your dance!</l>
<l>The Pot-Dancer, Govinda, who is stuck up with the pride of a king,</l>
<l>has taken our wealth.</l>
<l>Now, is this [act] of yours befitting?</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
